Variable Description: Number of registered voters in the constituency
The majority of votes by which the winning candidate won
Voter turnout in number of votes
Voter turnout as a percentage of registered voters

For parliamentary constituencies: 3 digit code of constituency (e.g. P125 for Putrajaya is coded 125). For state constituencies: 3 digit parliament code followed by 3 digit state constituency code (e.g. N33 for Air Itam (P51) in Penang is coded 051-033)
Variable Type: string (3 numerical digits for parliament, 3-3 for state)

Variable Description: Name of the state that the constituency belongs to
All variables that start with 'ethnicity_' shows the percentage of registered voters who belong to each ethnicity
